Page.PageName: Step 11&12- Sleep Test, Turn off Radiacmeter

Text.Value: • Return to Rate Mode by pressing the ON/OFF button until the display returns to the Rate Mode display
• The "SLEEP" indicator disappears
• The Radiacmeter is now ready for normal operation
Turning off the Radiacmeter:
• Press and hold the ON/OFF button until the display reads "OFF" followed by three horizontal bars
• Release the ON/OFF button
• The Radiacmeter is now off
Pre-operational testing is now complete and the radiacmeter is ready for normal operation.
